item.author: Jiajian Fu
item.description: The Chongqing University 3D Printing and Additive Manufacturing Association was established in October 2015 and is considered an A-level student organization at the university. We belong to the esteemed College of Mechanical Engineering. Our main focus lies in promoting and advancing the field of 3D printing and additive manufacturing.
